msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:267
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Filters`, and choose :guilabel:`Expiration Alerts`."
msgstr ""
"Klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Filters` en kies :guilabel:`Vervalmeldingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:None
msgid "Expiration alert for product past the expiration date."
msgstr "Vervalmelding voor product na de vervaldatum."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:274
msgid "Expiration notifications"
msgstr "Vervalmeldingen"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:276
msgid ""
"Users can be notified when the expiration date for a product has passed. "
"This can help keep specific employees up to date on the status of items "
"under their purview."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikers kunnen een melding ontvangen wanneer de vervaldatum van een "
"product is verstreken. Dit kan helpen om specifieke werknemers op de hoogte "
"te houden van de status van artikelen die onder hun verantwoordelijkheid "
"vallen."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:279
msgid ""
"To configure a notification, navigate to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Products --> Products`. Select a product configured with lot/serial numbers "
"and expiration date tracking. Navigate to the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab. "
"Under the :guilabel:`Logistics` section, select a user in "
"the :guilabel:`Responsible` field."
msgstr ""
"Om een melding te configureren, ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad app --> "
"Producten --> Producten`. Selecteer een product dat is geconfigureerd met "
"partij-/serienummers en het bijhouden van vervaldatums. Ga naar het "
"tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad`. Selecteer onder de "
"sectie :guilabel:`Logistiek` een gebruiker in het "
"veld :guilabel:`Verantwoordelijke`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:284
msgid ""
"When the expiation date passes for a lot/serial number for this product, a "
"notification is sent to the user in this field."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer de vervaldatum verstrijkt voor een partij/serienummer van dit "
"product, wordt er een melding verzonden naar de gebruiker in dit veld."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:288
msgid ""
"Once the expiration date is due, expiration alerts are created on the form "
"view of the lot/serial number of the product."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:291
msgid ""
"To customize these alerts, turn on :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, "
"go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Activity Types`, and "
"select the :guilabel:`Alert Date Reached` alert."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/expiration_dates.rst:295
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Default User` assigned will be notified once the expiration "
"date is reached. If no default user is configured, the activity will be "
"assigned to the :guilabel:`Responsible` user selected on the "
"product's :guilabel:`Inventory` tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:3
msgid "Lot numbers"
msgstr "Partijnummers"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:10
msgid ""
"*Lots* are one of the two ways to identify and track products in Odoo. They "
"typically represent a specific batch of products that were received, stored, "
"shipped, or manufactured in-house."
msgstr ""
"*Partijen* zijn een van de twee manieren om producten in Odoo te "
"identificeren en te volgen. Ze vertegenwoordigen doorgaans een specifieke "
"batch producten die zijn ontvangen, opgeslagen, verzonden of intern zijn "
"geproduceerd."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:13
msgid ""
"Manufacturers assign lot numbers to groups of products sharing common "
"properties, facilitating end-to-end traceability through their lifecycles."
msgstr ""
"Fabrikanten wijzen partijnummers toe aan groepen producten die "
"gemeenschappelijke eigenschappen delen, waardoor end-to-end traceerbaarheid "
"gedurende hun levenscyclus mogelijk wordt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:16
msgid ""
"Lots are useful for managing large quantities of manufactured or received "
"products, aiding in tracing items back to their group, particularly for "
"product recalls or :doc:`expiration dates <expiration_dates>`."
msgstr ""
"Partijen zijn nuttig voor het beheren van grote hoeveelheden gefabriceerde "
"of ontvangen producten en helpen bij het traceren van artikelen naar hun "
"groep, vooral voor productterugroepacties of :doc:`verloopdatums "
"<expiration_dates>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:26
msgid ""
"To track products using lots, enable the *Lots & Serial Numbers* feature. Go "
"to the :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`Traceability` section, and tick the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Lots & Serial Numbers`. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Activeer de functie *Partijen & serienummers* om producten met partijen te "
"volgen. Ga naar :menuselection:`Voorraad app --> Configuratie --> "
"Instellingen`, scroll naar beneden naar het "
"gedeelte :guilabel:`Traceerbaarheid` en vink het selectievakje aan "
"naast :guilabel:`Partijen & serienummers`. Klik vervolgens "
"op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:32
msgid ":doc:`Tracking expiration dates <expiration_dates>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Verloopdatums volgen <expiration_dates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:33
msgid ""
