"left corner. Doing so reveals a new, modifiable line on "
"the :guilabel:`Update Quantity` page. Then, input a desired lot number in "
"the :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number` field, and adjust the :guilabel:`On Hand "
"Quantity` to its original value."
