"gewenste naam in het veld :guilabel:`Locatienaam` in."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once the locations are named in alphabetical order, based on their proximity "
"to the output or packing location, set the removal strategy on "
"the :ref:`parent location <inventory/location-hierarchy>`."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de locaties alfabetisch zijn genaamd, gebaseerd op hun nabijheid tot "
"de uitvoer- of verpakkingslocatie, stel je de verwijderstrategie in op "
