#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:3
msgid "FEFO removal"
msgstr "FEFO-verwijdering"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *First Expired, First Out* (FEFO) removal strategy targets products for "
"removal based on their assigned removal dates."
msgstr ""
"De *First Expired, First Out* (FEFO) verwijderstrategie richt zich op "
"producten voor verwijdering op basis van hun toegewezen verwijderdata."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:14
msgid "Removal date"
msgstr "Verwijderdatum"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:16
msgid ""
"Products **must** be removed from inventory before their *removal date*, "
"which is set as a certain number of days before the product's *expiration "
"date*."
msgstr ""
"Producten **moeten** uit de voorraad worden verwijderd vóór hun "
"*verwijderdatum*, die is ingesteld als een bepaald aantal dagen vóór de "
"*vervaldatum* van het product."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:19
msgid ""
"The user sets this number of days by navigating to the product "
"form's :guilabel:`Inventory` tab. Under the :guilabel:`Traceability` "
"section, ensure the :guilabel:`Tracking` field is set to "
"either :guilabel:`By Lots` or :guilabel:`By Unique Serial Number`."
msgstr ""
"Je stelt dit aantal dagen in door te navigeren naar het "
"tabblad :guilabel:`Voorraad` van het productformulier. Zorg er onder de "
"sectie :guilabel:`Traceerbaarheid` voor dat het veld :guilabel:`Tracking` is "
"ingesteld op :guilabel:`Per partij` of :guilabel:`Per uniek serienummer`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:23
msgid ""
"Next, select the :guilabel:`Expiration Date` option, which makes "
"the :guilabel:`Removal Date` field (and other date fields) appear."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer vervolgens de optie :guilabel:`Vervaldatum`, waardoor het "
"veld :guilabel:`Verwijderdatum` (en andere datumvelden) verschijnt."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:27
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Lots and Serial Numbers` and :guilabel:`Expiration Dates` "
"features **must** be enabled in :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` to track expiration dates."
msgstr ""
"De functies :guilabel:`Partijen en serienummers` en :guilabel:`Vervaldatums` "
"**moeten** zijn ingeschakeld in :menuselection:`Voorraad-app --> "
"Configuratie --> Instellingen` om vervaldatums bij te houden."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:31
msgid ""
"The expiration date of a product is determined by adding the date the "
"product was received to the number of days specified in "
"the :guilabel:`Expiration Date` field of the product form."
msgstr ""
"De vervaldatum van een product wordt bepaald door de datum waarop het "
"product is ontvangen op te tellen bij het aantal dagen dat is opgegeven in "
"het veld :guilabel:`Vervaldatum` van het productformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:34
msgid ""
"The removal date takes this expiration date, and subtracts the number of "
"days specified in the :guilabel:`Removal Date` field of the product form."
msgstr ""
"De verwijderdatum neemt deze vervaldatum en trekt het aantal dagen af dat is "
"opgegeven in het veld :guilabel:`Verwijderdatum` van het productformulier."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:38
msgid ""
":doc:`Expiration dates <../../product_management/product_tracking/"
"expiration_dates>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Vervaldatums <../../product_management/product_tracking/"
"expiration_dates>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/fefo.rst:41
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory` tab of the product, `Egg`, the "
"following :guilabel:`Dates` are set by the user:"
